    <div class="crowd-tip"><strong>Best time:</strong> Tuesday, Wednesday, or Thursday morning for the quietest visit and easiest access to guided tours. Friday evenings draw a local crowd for evening programming but the museum is open until 21:00. Saturdays are the busiest day — arrive at opening (11:00) to secure a spot on the first guided tour.</div>
